\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 Illustration of our kids watching Shark Week a few weeks ago and then going to the beach \'96 they were scared of the wrong things.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \'93The reality is people are about as likely to die from a Sharknado (0.0 percent) as they are from a shark attack (1 in 3.7 million), according to the National Geographic Channel.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I\'92ve been thinking about this for a while, I think the church is a little like the NatGeo channel.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We\'92re talking about things in churches that while are interesting to some spectators\'85really don\'92t matter too much in day to day life.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 Transition:  But Jesus himself has told us the #1 killer of our walk with Him and God\'85and for years the church has ignored it and talked about so many other side issues like shark attacks, all the while His church is struggling\'85and all because it is awkward and hard to do.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf5 \'93No one can serve two masters.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus will either be Lord of all\'85or won\'92t be Lord at all!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf5 Either you will hate the one and love the other, or you will be devoted to the one and despise the other. You cannot serve both God and money.  Matt 6:24\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus says the biggest competitor for your heart and your walk with God is money\'85not lust, sex, drugs, rock n roll\'85it\'92s your stuff or the stuff you want!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it is so obvious because it is what the church needs to talk about but never do because people get upset and say things like \'91All the church wants is my money\'92.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I hope I can disprove that myth today and I\'92m going to do it with an illustration that on some level every parent has had at some point if your kids are old enough.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Illustration of Chris and I and the skittles\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 3 Things he didn\'92t realize or want to admit in that moment:\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I was the one who gave him the skittles in the first place.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I was bigger than him and if I really wanted them I could physically take them.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I was richer than him and if I wanted to I could give him as many skittles as he could eat for a year.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 1)  I was the one who gave him them in the first place\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf5 \super 18\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But remember the\'a0Lord\'a0your God, for it is he who gives you the ability to produce wealth, and so confirms his covenant, which he swore to your ancestors, as it is today.  Deut 8:18\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God gave you everything you have in the first place!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God ties your ability to earn a living to his goodness toward you and how much He loves you.	\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So if God gave it to you why does he want part of it back?\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1440\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf8 Illustration of parent giving kids a phone or game\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf8 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}So you take it away because the thing that should have been a good thing you gave them in the first place becomes a god in their world and it is interrupting the relationship between the two of you.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God has given us money to use because He loves us\'85but the problem is there is a temptation for us to turn what is good into a god.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God wants to remove the grip of greed that can consume us if we\'92re not careful\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 2)  I was bigger than him and if I really wanted it I could physically take it\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf5 \super 3\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub In the course of time Cain brought some of the fruits of the soil as an offering\'a0to the\'a0Lord.\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 4\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub And Abel also brought an offering\'97fat portions\'a0from some of the firstborn of his flock.\'a0The\'a0Lord\'a0looked with favor on Abel and his offering,\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 5\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub but on Cain and his offering he did not look with favor. So Cain was very angry, and his face was downcast.  Genesis 3\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I love the end of that\'85Cain\'92s face was downcast and he was angry.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is the people in the current church who say \'91Church just wants my money\'92.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They are pleasant until you mention money\'85because it\'92s their god.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 6\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Then the\'a0Lord\'a0said to Cain, \'93Why are you angry?\'a0Why is your face downcast?\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 7\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub If you do what is right, will you not be accepted? But if you do not do what is right, sin is crouching at your door;\'a0it desires to have you, but you must rule over it.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Notice God\'92s response to Cain keeping back what he should have given to God\'85it\'92s a conversation not condemnation or control.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God doesn\'92t but in and go \'91OK, you\'92ve proven I can\'92t trust you\'85I\'92m going to take it all away now\'92.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf7 3)  I was richer than he was\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf5 \super 9\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub You are under a curse\'97your whole nation\'97because you are robbing me.\

\f0\b\fs18 \super 10\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Bring the whole tithe\'a0into the storehouse,\'a0that there may be food in my house. Test me in this,\'94 says the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty,\
\'93and see if I will not throw open the floodgates\'a0of heaven and pour out\'a0so much blessing\'a0that there will not be room enough to store it.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs18 \cf5 \super 11\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I will prevent pests from devouring\'a0your crops, and the vines in your fields will not drop their fruit before it is ripe,\'94 says the\'a0Lord\'a0Almighty.  Malachi 3\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}God says He can and will prevent things from happening to you that happen to others when we trust Him and put Him first in our finances.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
