\f0\b \cf4 Transition:  I know some people are in here thinking\'85this is OT stuff Nic and we aren\'92t under the law any more\'85we\'92re in the NT now.  \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs18 \cf5 \super 42\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub \'93Woe to you Pharisees, because you give God a tenth\'a0of your mint, rue and all other kinds of garden herbs, but you neglect justice and the love of God.\'a0You should have practiced the latter without leaving the former undone.  Luke 11\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0\cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Jesus told the Jews to tithe\'85it\'92s interesting how so many Christians want only do what Jesus says and ignore the rest of the Bible unless it comes to money\'85and then they point to we are under grace!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And we are under grace\'85and if you\'92re response to God grace \'96 which is that you were God\'92s enemy and God loved you so much he sent His son to physically live a hard life that was perfect, only to be brutally beaten for you and then end up murdered on a cross for YOUR sins\'85He died for you\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If your response to God\'92s grace and gift to you is \'91Well technically then do I still have to give to Him now that we\'92re under grace?\'92\'85SHAME ON YOU!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Do I believe you have to give 10% of your income or God will get mad and curse you\'85nope. \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I do think it is a good principle though and I know grace always calls us to a deeper commitment to God, not less.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I believe we are called to give generously and a percentage from a grateful heart\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 You should follow the same procedure I gave to the churches in Galatia.\'a0
\f0\b\fs18 \super 2\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub On the first day of each week, you should each put aside a portion of the money you have earned. Don\'92t wait until I get there and then try to collect it all at once.\'a0  \
1 Cor 16: 1-2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s percentage based\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s decided ahead of time\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s consistent\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
