\f0\b \cf4 Translation:  Here is what all this means for our church\'85\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 YOU\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want you to do two things\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pay it Forward\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}As a church we are starting the third leg of our Change the World ministry\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Pay it forward for you to give generously\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We will have envelopes that we will hand out to you as you leave.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want to bless the city and for them to know why\'85because God calls us to be generous and we live out that principle in our daily lives, not just on Sundays.\
\pard\tx2380\tx2880\pardeftab720\li2880\fi-2880\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl3\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Give examples of ways people can use these envelopes.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}(sit here for a few seconds to make sure people know what we are asking of them)\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ask the question:  What is God calling you to give?\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not are you giving\'85no Cain gave and got really grumpy cat like when God said that wasn\'92t the point\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl2
\f0\b \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The question is God Lord of all\'85including your money.\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
